nhc_headline: ...HENRIETTE EXPECTED TO BECOME A POST-TROPICAL CYCLONE ON WEDNESDAY...
summary: ...HENRIETTE EXPECTED TO BECOME A POST-TROPICAL CYCLONE ON WEDNESDAY... As of 11:00 AM HST Tue Aug 12 the center of Henriette was located near 34.1, -162.9 with movement NW at 18 mph. The minimum central pressure was 999 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 65 mph.
